Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Inflation rising again
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b0440fjl
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 9 Aug 1987
Thatcher refuses to back Reagan over US naval involvement in the Persian Gulf as oil price rises boost inflation. The sound quality on this recording is variable/poor. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less